data.description: Stunning 4-bed, 3-bath beauty. Step inside, and you'll be greeted by the sheer elegance of granite countertops in the kitchen and bathrooms. Arches throughout. The kitchen features a long breakfast bar. Recessed lighting and stylish plant ledges. Each of the four bedrooms comes with its very own walk-in closet. Tile flooring throughout. 3-car garage with extra depth. The lot size is 14,666sf. View Lot. Veteran to Veteran 2.75% on current balance. Ask about seller paying buyers closing costs.
